AREA AREAS

Here at Age of Legends, we have tried to implement areas (or zones)
which replicate some of the famous landmarks in Pre-Cataclysm Ansalon.
We have also put in areas which conform to the map of Pre-Cataclysm
Ansalon. Thus, you will find Palanthas and other cities, as well
as the Dargaard Mountains and Vingaard Keep. We are constantly putting
in new zones to keep you the player interested in the mud. Read the
boards on a frequent basis for information as to new zones.

See also: DRAGONLANCE
