BOARDS BOARD

Bulletin boards are the forum of inter-player communication on the MUD.
There are different bulletin boards for different purposes -- for example,
an out of character board, a trade board for people wanting to buy and 
sell items, a bug board to report bugs, etc.

Type "LOOK BOARD" to see the messages already posted on a board.  Type
"WRITE <subject>" to post a message to a board. Type "READ <number>" to
read a post, and type "REMOVE <number>" to remove your own messages.

NOTE: When you are finished writing your message on the board and you
want to save it type /s.

Example:

  > look at board
  > write Am I using these boards correctly?
  > look at board
  > read 6
  > remove 6

See also: MAIL, READ, WRITE
#
CLAN CLANS

Clans on Age of Legends are player run. We have the traditional Dragonlance
clans including the Knights of Solamnia as well as the Conclave of Wizards.
Should you choose to join one of these organizations, simple make a post
on the Main Board in any city or ask a passing player. Please also note that
it is possible to start your own clan as long as the idea fits within the
Dragonlance environment. For example, the Forest Warriors have been formed
which is open to Druids and Rangers.

See also: ROLEPLAY, DRAGONLANCE
