CLASSES CLASS

At Age of Legends we have implemented most of the popular Dragonlance classes.
These incude mages, clerics, druids, rogues, rangers, paladins, fighters
and knights. FOr more information on classes here at Age of Legends, visit
our website at http://agelegends.planetmud.com/.

