GUILD GUILDS

Guilds are places where people come to learn and practice the skills and spells
of their particular trade.  Note that guilds are not exclusive - ie, a rogue can
train in the mage's guild, and a priest could learn from the fighte's guild, 
providing the character can get there in the first place.

