MAGE WIZARD

Mages are beings who use the power of the magical weave to cast spells.  Most
of a mage's spells are offensive in nature, from the well-known magic missile
spell to the explosive fireball and the deadly meteor swarm - mages are not
known for their healing abilities in general.

All mages draw their power from the moons of Krynn - Solinari, the White Moon,
Lunitari, the Red Moon, and Nuitari, the Black Moon.  Each of the three gods
of the moon oversees a particular alignment of mage - as a result of this, a
mage's spells, especially at high levels, will differ greatly depending on that
mage's alignment.

See also: PRACTICE, SPELLS, CAST, MEM
